latestPosts.caption:
Healing isn’t always pretty.
No one prepares you for the emotional weight of watching your skin change—breakouts, dullness, flare-ups.
But I’m learning that progress isn’t always linear, and that’s okay.
You are not your bad skin days. You are growing, healing, and still so worthy.
If you’re going through it too—just know, you’re not alone.🤍 This reel was inspired by a creator ( lost the reel can’t tag her, will tag her if I found it again )
